
//Lecture no. 38
//Navigation with React Native (same as React route in ReactJs)(web development me routing kahte h aur app development me Navigation).

Types of Navigation
1.Stack(Ek page se dusre page me jane ke liye hota h jaise login page, signup page)
2.Drawer(e.g:-side me menu hota hai us pe click karne pe bahut sara list aata h jaise gmail me hota h)
3.Tab  e.g:-Whattsapp(chat,status hota hai)

3.1 Bottom Tab Navigation(means option bottom me rahega jaise amazon me dekhte h n option niche me rahta h jaise Home Transaction etc)
3.2 Top Tab Navigation (means top me option rahega jaise WhatsApp me rahta h n chat status call upper me usko top tab navigation bolte h)



dependencies we have to add in snack dev
{
  "dependencies": {
    "@expo/vector-icons": "^14.0.2",
    "react-native-paper": "4.9.2",
    "react-native-screens": "~4.4.0",
    "@react-navigation/stack": "*",
    "@react-navigation/native": "*",
    "react-native-gesture-handler": "~2.20.2",
    "react-native-safe-area-context": "4.12.0"
  }
}
